description:
Hellblade 2 is undeniably a technically amazing game, but it that enough to make it a good game?

Hellblade 2 launch to divided reviews. While critics unanimously praised the game for its visual and audible presentation, they were torn on how engaging its gameplay was.

In this week's episode of Spot On, Tam and Lucy discuss what Hellblade 2's technical achievements bring to the game, and if graphics alone are the marker of a quality title.

#gaming #gamespot #hellblade2
title: Hellblade 2: Graphics vs Gameplay
